data.description: Introducing this charming and fully updated 3/2 at an outstanding central location in Fort Walton Beach. You will enjoy quick and easy access to Eglin AFB, Hurlburt Field and Duke Field, as well as countless dining and shopping options. This home is move-in ready and features a new roof and fresh paint throughout. You'll love the master bedroom's unique coffered ceilings and one-way glass French doors. This home must be seen in person to be appreciated! No HOA and no flood insurance required.|| Video walkthrough can be seen here:  https://youtu.be/twsuc0VNroI?si=dqZuizzjr6oj4cQi ||Security cameras and washer and dryer will convey. Call today to arrange a visit!
